      "content": "i know i should talk to a doctor eventually but i hate going to the clinic just for this and they usually just tell me to stick with it anyway. like i've been on the zoloft for a few months now so i'm not exactly \"starting\" it. wouldn't it be okay to just take it one day and then start the st johns wort the next day? just to get the nausea to stop? i really want to avoid those pharmaceutical chemicals if i can.",
